OL,7,FTour de France champion Chris Froome
OL,8,Fis "in good spirits" after undergoing
OL,9,Fsurgery following a 'serious crash'.
OL,11,FThe British cyclist was on a training
OL,12,Fride on Wednesday when the accident
OL,13,Fhappened and was taken by helicopter
OL,14,Fto a hospital in Toulon on the French
OL,15,FRiviera.
OL,17,FIt left him with a fractured
OL,18,Fvertebrae, collapsed lung and five
OL,19,Fbroken ribs.
