OL,7,FA statement on Froome's official X
OL,8,Fprofile read: "We can confirm that
OL,9,FChris has successfully undergone
OL,10,Fsurgery following his recent injuries.
OL,12,F"The procedure went as planned, and
OL,13,FChris is currently recovering in
OL,14,Fhospital under the care of his medical
OL,15,Fteam.
OL,17,F"He is in good spirits and grateful
OL,18,Ffor the excellent medical support he
OL,19,Fhas received.
